snippet.title: Classic Games - Tanaka 3D Gameplay
snippet.description:
Only found 1 video of this game on youtube.

Truly a forgotten gem. Damn, i used to spend HOURS playing this. Customization in this game is awesome and there are LOTS of cars, weapons etc.
Sorry for the slight fuck-ups, i haven't played this game in a long time. Apparently, you can go sanic fast too by using a glitch (sadly, didn't get it on video tho)

Game was made by by Pacific Media WorkX in 1999

If you want to see more of this game, hit me up.
